{"tid":218280,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[敬拜] 有無人好敬佩自己個女朋友","createTime":"2017-04-26T11:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T19:33:57.000Z","uid":32699,"like":87,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf796f628d1f8ceaa6bd41b7d280285a6897c34","tid":218280,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"尋日同佢23個月 忽然諗起自己個女朋友好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係大學生<br />\n但識講流利使用4種既語言 + 2種鄉下話 (福建 &amp; 客家) <br />\n自稱英文唔叻但可以係英語流行既地方做2年文員 + 讀書<br />\n而家無聊自學緊韓文<br />\n極高既創意 改圖又叻<br />\n又有生意頭腦<br />\n以前細細個15歲就已經係fb搞網購搵左筆<br />\n人又古靈精怪 講野又醒目 <br />\n講野成日比佢暗暗兜個圈話返我 然後奸笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要幾靚女 有時都唔明點解會揀我呢D零家底又無咩才能既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時諗 到底我比唔比到幸運佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有D無自信"},{"pid":"2fe4bcc8fedaff929332d96c42bdf38518fef849","tid":218280,"uid":107472,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:38:55.000Z","msg":"你試下大大力搣下自己  唔痛嫁"},{"pid":"7e65e2b429574c4359843953a27735299af6e16f","tid":218280,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:39:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你試下大大力搣下自己  唔痛嫁</blockquote><br />\n我有時都唔信自己呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b894b918747945a8dddd13e298e0a546e64dfe","tid":218280,"uid":105060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:40:14.000Z","msg":"成日唔食藥"},{"pid":"2058def84b15932cbb8e9f9fe67e1fb1f552575f","tid":218280,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"我有相熟醫生 <br />\n樓主需唔需要？"},{"pid":"4e8f0181746f7c3931e1b6b36638c0e55bf52b34","tid":218280,"uid":83933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:42:23.000Z","msg":"簡得你代表你一定有吸引佢既原因,比D信心增值下自己啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49c5ec22d9c85c4999ffc3affaeb998fe4bc9ee","tid":218280,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:42:33.000Z","msg":"我認真開post嫁<br />\n到底呢度仲有無同路人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2be106163fe29dd3988ee3b225599fe414786c","tid":218280,"uid":55874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:43:42.000Z","msg":"好鐘意女仔講嘢精靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日串返你但係係令人覺得好笑個種串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610493824a380e5b48a84c7ecd4ccfe1ff080525","tid":218280,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡得你代表你一定有吸引佢既原因,比D信心增值下自己啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左兒時玩伴之外諗唔到其他原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過當初用左好大勇氣追佢返黎就真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用情信"},{"pid":"0a8ab3fdefd180f65fbf9a5f47ca5e52d381ea30","tid":218280,"uid":44153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:45:05.000Z","msg":"咁你努力唔好比女友拋太遠.."},{"pid":"48ff03ff7a2485ea6549b325a1b79351e8f6a088","tid":218280,"uid":52891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:45:40.000Z","msg":"佢溝你？<br />\n你好靚仔？<br />\n你講野好叻？"},{"pid":"6526db79d0670aed548dbb769b90a6d25af04ac4","tid":218280,"uid":32699,"like":0,"di